Post title: IMS/CP viewer and iOS
Post description: iOS devices (iPhone, iPad) currently cannot display the contents of an IMS/CP package in a scrollable way, i.e. the top of the contents is visible, but you cannot scroll down in the viewer's sub-window. Other sources cite similar problems with iOS when trying to view <iframe> contents - they're not scrollable. I suspect that the same underlying problem is responsible for both cases, even though the IMS/CP viewer uses an <object> to display the contents. Does anyone have more information on this issue, or even a workaround?
